@node intro "IntuiSup/Intro"
This is a quick reference guide for the Intuition Support Library (ISUP).

ISUP is a shared library so you have to make a call to `OpenLibrary' before
using the Library in your code. Also you have to include the header file
`intuisup.h'.

We have made an @{"index" link funcs} table to all function, to get easy access to the
description of the functions.

Last the @{"Data Structures and Defines" link data} are also describe. 
@endnode


